	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false) ~> eventClass
clinicalevent, updatePrsnl join(VERIFIED_PRSNL_ID == updatePrsnl@PERSON_ID,
	joinType:'inner',
	broadcast: 'none')~> cePrsnlUpdatePersonnel
cePrsnlUpdatePersonnel, updatePrsnl, verifiedPrsnl join(VERIFIED_PRSNL_ID == verifiedprsnl@PERSON_ID,
	joinType:'inner',
	broadcast: 'none')~> cePrsnlVerifiedPersonnel
cePrsnlVerifiedPersonnel, performingPrsnl join(ERROR_FUNCTION('') == ERROR_FUNCTION(''),
	joinType:'inner',
	broadcast: 'none')~> cePrsnlPerformingPersonnel
cePrsnlPerformingPersonnel, eventClass join(EVENT_CD == CODE_VALUE
	&& ERROR_FUNCTION('') == ERROR_FUNCTION(''),
	joinType:'inner',
	broadcast: 'none')~> ceEventCode
eventClass filter(ERROR_FUNCTION('')) ~> Filter1
